# Regenerable process artifacts written by the subagents during a run.
# They are the inter-agent bus, not source of truth — keep them local.
# The signed contracts (features/*.feature) and the spec (project-spec.md)
# ARE tracked; only the progress/ reports are ignored.
progress/*
!progress/current.md
